snippet.title: Bionic Bay - PS5 Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description: Featuring stunning high-detail pixel art, tight and precise platforming, and chaotic physics-based gameplay, Bionic Bay tasks players with escaping an ancient biomechanical world filled with imaginative technology and deadly traps. It's coming to PS5 in 2025.
